=== EVENT_ROSETTA_PROBE ===
# id: 47
# title: Rosetta Probe
# chinese_title: 罗塞塔探针
# category: LanguageChallenge
# mode: starmap

You recover an ancient probe designed to teach language through images and symbols. It cycles through radical characters with their meanings.

* [Study the radical for 'person' (人)]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  人 (rén) — person
* [Study the radical for 'mouth' (口)]
  ~ gain_radical("口")
  口 (kǒu) — mouth
* [Study the radical for 'sun' (日)]
  ~ gain_radical("日")
  日 (rì) — sun/day
* [Download all data for later study]
  ~ gain_credits(5)
  下载 (xiàzài) — download
